[
  {
    "bookname": "Amos",
    "chapter": "8",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">The <st data-num=\"0136\" class=\"\">Sovereign</st> <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">showed</st> me <st data-num=\"03541\" class=\"\">this</st>: I <st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">saw</st><n id=\"1\" /> a <st data-num=\"03619\" class=\"\">basket</st> of <st data-num=\"07019\" class=\"\">summer fruit</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> ",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Amos",
    "chapter": "8",
    "text": "He <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">What</st> do <st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">you</st> <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">see</st>, <st data-num=\"05986\" class=\"\">Amos</st>?\u201d I <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">replied</st>, \u201cA <st data-num=\"03619\" class=\"\">basket</st> of <st data-num=\"07019\" class=\"\">summer fruit</st>.\u201d Then the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> me, \u201cThe <st data-num=\"07093\" class=\"\">end</st><n id=\"1\" /> has <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">come</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">for</st> my <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>! I will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">no</st> <st data-num=\"03254 05750\">longer</st> <st data-num=\"05674\" class=\"\">overlook</st> their sins.<n id=\"2\" /></p>",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Amos",
    "chapter": "8",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">The <st data-num=\"07892\" class=\"\">women singing</st> in the <st data-num=\"01964\" class=\"\">temple</st><n id=\"1\" /> will <st data-num=\"03213\" class=\"\">wail</st> in <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">that</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st>.\u201d <p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"0136\" class=\"\">Sovereign</st> <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> is <st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">speaking</st>. <p class=\"poetry\">\u201cThere will be <st data-num=\"07227\" class=\"\">many</st> <st data-num=\"06297\" class=\"\">corpses</st> <st data-num=\"07993\" class=\"\">littered</st> <st data-num=\"03605 04725 \">everywhere</st>!<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"02013\" class=\"\">Be quiet</st>!\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Amos",
    "chapter": "8",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">Listen to</st> <st data-num=\"02063\" class=\"\">this</st>, you who <st data-num=\"07602\" class=\"\">trample</st><n id=\"1\" /> the <st data-num=\"034\" class=\"\">needy</st><p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"07673\" class=\"\">do away with</st><n id=\"2\" /> the <st data-num=\"06035\" class=\"\">destitute</st> in the <st data-num=\"06041\" class=\"\">land</st>.</p>",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Amos",
    "chapter": "8",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">You <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">say</st>, <p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"04970\" class=\"\">When</st> will the <st data-num=\"02320\" class=\"\">new moon festival</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"05674\" class=\"\">be over</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> so we can <st data-num=\"07666\" class=\"\">sell</st> <st data-num=\"07668\" class=\"\">grain</st>? <p class=\"poetry\">When will the <st data-num=\"07676\" class=\"\">Sabbath</st> end,<n id=\"3\" /> so we can <st data-num=\"06605\" class=\"\">open up</st> the <st data-num=\"01250\" class=\"\">grain</st> bins?<n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">We\u2019re eager<n id=\"5\" /> to <st data-num=\"0374\" class=\"\">sell</st> <st data-num=\"06994\" class=\"\">less</st> for a <st data-num=\"01431\" class=\"\">higher</st> <st data-num=\"08255\" class=\"\">price</st>,<n id=\"6\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and to <st data-num=\"05791\" class=\"\">cheat</st> the buyer <st data-num=\"05791\" class=\"\">with</st> <st data-num=\"04820\" class=\"\">rigged</st> <st data-num=\"03976\" class=\"\">scales</st>!<n id=\"7\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Amos",
    "chapter": "8",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">We\u2019re eager to <st data-num=\"07069\" class=\"\">trade</st> <st data-num=\"03701\" class=\"\">silver</st> for the <st data-num=\"01800\" class=\"\">poor</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">a pair of <st data-num=\"05275\" class=\"\">sandals</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"05668\" class=\"\">for</st> the <st data-num=\"034\" class=\"\">needy</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">We want to <st data-num=\"07666\" class=\"\">mix in</st> some <st data-num=\"04651\" class=\"\">chaff</st> with the <st data-num=\"01250\" class=\"\">grain</st>!\u201d<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Amos",
    "chapter": "8",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"07650\" class=\"\">confirms this oath</st><n id=\"1\" /> by the <st data-num=\"01347\" class=\"\">arrogance</st> of <st data-num=\"03290\" class=\"\">Jacob</st>:<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u201cI <st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">swear</st><n id=\"3\" /> I will <st data-num=\"0518 05331\">never</st> <st data-num=\"07911\" class=\"\">forget</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> you have <st data-num=\"04639\" class=\"\">done</st>!<n id=\"4\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Amos",
    "chapter": "8",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">Because of</st> <st data-num=\"02063\" class=\"\">this</st> the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">earth</st><n id=\"1\" /> will <st data-num=\"03808 07264\">quake</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> who <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">live</st> in it will <st data-num=\"056\" class=\"\">mourn</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">whole</st> earth<n id=\"3\" /> will <st data-num=\"05927\" class=\"\">rise</st> like the <st data-num=\"02975\" class=\"\">Nile River</st>;<n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">it will <st data-num=\"01644\" class=\"\">surge upward</st><n id=\"5\" /> and then <st data-num=\"08257\" class=\"\">grow calm</st>,<n id=\"6\" /> like the <st data-num=\"02975\" class=\"\">Nile</st> in <st data-num=\"04714\" class=\"\">Egypt</st>.<n id=\"7\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Amos",
    "chapter": "8",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">In <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">that</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st>,\u201d <st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">says</st> the <st data-num=\"0136\" class=\"\">Sovereign</st> <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, \u201cI will <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">make</st> the <st data-num=\"08121\" class=\"\">sun</st> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">set</st> at <st data-num=\"06672\" class=\"\">noon</st><p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"02821\" class=\"\">make</st> the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">earth</st> <st data-num=\"02821\" class=\"\">dark</st> in the <st data-num=\"0216\" class=\"\">middle</st> of the <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Amos",
    "chapter": "8",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"02015\" class=\"\">turn</st> your <st data-num=\"02282\" class=\"\">festivals</st> into <st data-num=\"060\" class=\"\">funerals</st><n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> your <st data-num=\"07892\" class=\"\">songs</st> into <st data-num=\"07015\" class=\"\">funeral dirges</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">I will make <st data-num=\"03605 04975\">everyone</st> <st data-num=\"05927 05921\">wear</st> <st data-num=\"08242\" class=\"\">funeral clothes</st><n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">cause</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">every</st> <st data-num=\"07218\" class=\"\">head</st> to be shaved <st data-num=\"07144\" class=\"\">bald</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"07760\" class=\"\">make</st> you <st data-num=\"060\" class=\"\">mourn</st> as if you had lost your <st data-num=\"03173\" class=\"\">only son</st>;<n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">when it <st data-num=\"0319\" class=\"\">ends</st> it will indeed have been a <st data-num=\"04751\" class=\"\">bitter</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st>.<n id=\"5\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Amos",
    "chapter": "8",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">Be certain of this</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> the <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">time</st> is<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">coming</st>,\u201d <st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">says</st> the <st data-num=\"0136\" class=\"\">Sovereign</st> <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, <p class=\"poetry\">\u201cwhen I will <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">send</st> a <st data-num=\"07458\" class=\"\">famine</st> through the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st>\u2014<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> a <st data-num=\"07458\" class=\"\">shortage</st> of <st data-num=\"03899\" class=\"\">food</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">or</st> <st data-num=\"06772 04325\">water</st><p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588 0518\">but</st> an <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">end</st> to <st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">divine</st> <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">revelation</st>.<n id=\"3\" /></p>",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Amos",
    "chapter": "8",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">People<n id=\"1\" /> will <st data-num=\"05128\" class=\"\">stagger</st> from <st data-num=\"03220\" class=\"\">sea</st> <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"03220\" class=\"\">sea</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and from the <st data-num=\"06828\" class=\"\">north</st> around <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">to</st> the <st data-num=\"04217\" class=\"\">east</st>. <p class=\"poetry\">They will <st data-num=\"07751\" class=\"\">wander about</st> <st data-num=\"01245\" class=\"\">looking</st> for a <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">message</st> from the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, <p class=\"poetry\">but they will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"04672\" class=\"\">find</st> any.<n id=\"3\" /></p>",
    "verse": "12"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Amos",
    "chapter": "8",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">In <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">that</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st> your<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"03303\" class=\"\">beautiful</st> <st data-num=\"01330\" class=\"\">young women</st><n id=\"2\" /> and your<n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"0970\" class=\"\">young men</st> will <st data-num=\"05968\" class=\"\">faint</st> from <st data-num=\"06772\" class=\"\">thirst</st>.<n id=\"4\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "13"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Amos",
    "chapter": "8",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">These are the ones who now <st data-num=\"07650\" class=\"\">take oaths</st><n id=\"1\" /> in the name of the <st data-num=\"0819\" class=\"\">sinful</st> idol goddess<n id=\"2\" /> of <st data-num=\"08111\" class=\"\">Samaria</st>. <p class=\"poetry\">They <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">vow</st>,<n id=\"3\" /> \u2018As surely as your <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">god</st><n id=\"4\" /> <st data-num=\"02416\" class=\"\">lives</st>, O <st data-num=\"01835\" class=\"\">Dan,\u2019</st> or, \u2018As surely as your <st data-num=\"01730\" class=\"\">beloved one</st><n id=\"5\" /> <st data-num=\"02416\" class=\"\">lives</st>, O <st data-num=\"0884\" class=\"\">Beer Sheba</st>!\u2019 <p class=\"poetry\">But they will <st data-num=\"05307\" class=\"\">fall down</st> and <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">get up</st> <st data-num=\"05750\" class=\"\">again</st>.\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "14"
  }
]